---
title: Hearty All-American Pork Meatball Sub with Avocado Salad & Potato Fries
description: Indulge in the bold flavours of this sub, where succulent pork meatballs are nestled within a soft, toasted brioche bun with garlic aioli and creamy avocado. Accompanied by crunchy fries, this dish offers a tantalizing fusion of American spices and savoury goodness that’s sure to have you coming back for seconds!
